<p>The Molly's Game actor, who has been isolated since finding out that 
he had been exposed to someone who tested positive, said in the video, 
"So, I'm here because of my production, and the doctor and medic team 
for the production were contacted because someone that I was in contact 
with, who is also in the public eye, tested positive." The 
aforementioned person is thought to be Justin Trudeau's wife Sophie, who
 was photographed with Mr Elba at a public event.</p>
